          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，李克用。自灭黄巢以来，收了一十三家太保，圣上见喜，封我为晋王，恩"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐龙楼凤阁，众家太保朝贺，只许称孤，不许道寡，这且不言。今奉圣上之命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巡查河南、河北。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众太保！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝、周德威、史敬思",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马可曾齐备？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝、周德威、史敬思",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俱已齐备。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵发潼关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝、周德威、史敬思",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前道为何不行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此潼关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝、周德威、史敬思",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马列开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "存孝听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领一哨人马，巡查河北，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父子哪里相会？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "独立岗前相会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父子潼关分人马，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李存孝下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李克用",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "独立岗前扎大营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周德威、史敬思",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，安营下寨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
