    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "王彦章"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王彦章上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "面带杀气鬼神愁，黄河两旁度春秋。两膀能有千斤力，嚇退黄河水倒流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，王彦章。自幼生成两膀能有千斤膂力。霸占黄河摆渡营生。今闻李家父子，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巡查河南、河北一带地方，存孝小儿从此经过。不免夺他一哨人马，反上大"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唐。就是这个主意，就此走遭也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼生来不可挡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全凭铁篙把人伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "专等存孝小儿郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王彦章下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "念": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.0,
        0.4286,
        0.4286,
        0.1429,
        0.0,
        1,
        0.0,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四龙套",
        "李存孝",
        "王彦章"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、李存孝同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼生来性刚强，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此黄河。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马列开。传稍水。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传稍水。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "（内西皮导板） 黄河两岸闹嚷嚷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王彦章上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了铁篙王彦章。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "稍水，为何不摆爷的官兵过河？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给了银两，渡尔等过河。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且问你霸住黄河，可有圣上的旨意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有部文？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔霸住黄河全凭何物？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全凭手中铁篙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你那铁篙可有多重？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五百余斤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔为何发笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我笑尔坐井观天。王爷帐下军校常使用八百斤兵器。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔休夸大口。着打！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王彦章败下，李存孝追下。王彦章上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，某家不曾提防，反被小儿一篙打下水去。不免挡住三岔路口，定要与他"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才是我未提防，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李存孝追上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼人敢把黄河挡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，存孝，我的儿！王爷挡住三岔路口，定要与尔决个胜负。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢说尔是一员将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任尔雪山高万丈，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手执铁篙朝下打，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷接篙不慌忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷饶命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可惜尔是少年郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷今日将我放，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本该今日将你放，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "日后我把大唐反，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王彦章看铁篙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这铁篙好似弯弓样，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李存孝笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒被小儿笑一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用手将篙忙搭上，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王彦章看铁篙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王彦章",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "铁篙好似随风长，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王彦章下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李存孝",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放了黄河稍水将，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李存孝、四龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
