    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众将与爷展旗号",
        "旗牌",
        "朱温"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。四下手、四扎头、朱温同上。〖点绛唇〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忆昔当年不可挡，雅观楼前摆战场。存孝与我夺袍带，某家一怒反朝纲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，大梁王朱温。在唐室为臣，御赐全忠。唐王见喜，在雅观楼前大摆筵宴，"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庆贺功臣。可恨存孝小儿，与孤抓袍夺带，羞辱某家。是某一时怒忿不过，带"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领人马，反出朝歌。今闻李家父子巡查河北。也曾命人打听，不知军中可有存"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孝无有。怎么还不见到来？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人行千里路，马过万重山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人交令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔回来了？打听军中，可有存孝无有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁，小人打听存孝巡查河北去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军中并无存孝。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱温笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说军中无存孝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由某家喜眉梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐心努力反皇朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将与爷展旗号"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何阻令？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀千岁：要拿克用，须得定计而行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔有何妙计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁修书一封，请他父子前来赴瑞宝大会。军中设下金钟一口，金钟一响，军"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "食战饭；金钟二响，众将披挂整齐；金钟三响，众将一起下手，拿住他父子，"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂不是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱温",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计甚好。掩门，后帐修书。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
